# Regression Tables via `pf.etable()`

## Basic Usage

We can compare all regression models via the pyfixest-internal `pf.etable()` function:

::: {#a94799cc .cell execution_count=2}
``` {.python .cell-code}
pf.etable([fit1, fit2, fit3, fit4, fit5, fit6])
```

