You can also estimate and display multiple regressions with one line of code using the (py)fixest stepwise notation:

::: {#0f775a19 .cell execution_count=3}
``` {.python .cell-code}
pf.etable(pf.feols("Y+Y2~csw(X1,X2,X1:X2)", data=data))
```

