::: {#1d1d5e21 .cell execution_count=29}
``` {.python .cell-code}
DTable(
    data,
    vars=["Y", "Y2", "X1", "X2"],
    labels=labels,
    bycol=["country"],
    byrow="occupation",
    stats=["count", "mean", "std"],
    caption="Descriptive statistics",
)
```

